title: Sacramento Jordan Peterson Meetup May 6 Invitation
description:
We're meeting at Living Stones Church. 1390 Florin Rd. Sacramento CA 95822 at 5pm on May 6 2018. 

https://www.meetup.com/Sacramento-Jordan-Peterson-Meetup/events/249464112/
